          "text": "得令！"
        },
        {
          "character": "袁绍",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且住！颜良被红脸大汉，刀劈落马，定是刘备之弟关羽所为。\n来，传刘备进帐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四文堂",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刘备进帐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘备上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "盟主帐中唤一声，\n倒叫刘备犯叮咛。\n盟主发怒为何情？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见盟主。"
        },
        {
          "character": "迈步且把宝帐进、袁绍",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唗，大胆刘备，我大将颜良，被红脸大汉，刀劈落马，定是你二弟关云长所为！\n来啊，将刘备推出斩了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且慢，容备一言奉告。"
        },
        {
          "character": "袁绍",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "讲！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "明公只听一面之词，而绝往日之情耶？备自徐州失散，二弟云长未知存亡，天\n下同貌者颇多，岂赤面长髯之人，即为云长？望公思之。"
        },
        {
          "character": "袁绍",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唔呼呀，不是使君明言，险些误伤好人。使君起过一旁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢明公。"
        },
        {
          "character": "文丑",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（文丑上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "文丑",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哇呀……"
        },
        {
          "character": "文丑",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听说颜良把命丧，\n不由某家怒满堂。\n迈步且把宝帐上——"
        },
        {
          "character": "文丑",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "主帅！"
        },
        {
          "character": "文丑",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "誓与颜良报冤枉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "文丑",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "主帅，探马报道，颜良被红脸大汉，刀劈落马。末将愿讨一支将令，与颜良报\n仇雪恨啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "袁绍",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军有此胆量？"
        },
        {
          "character": "文丑",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有此胆量！"
        },
        {
          "character": "袁绍",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，命你带领三万人马，与颜良报仇雪恨，不得有误！"
        },
        {
          "character": "文丑",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且慢，文将军，备愿相助于你。"
        },
        {
          "character": "文丑",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "住了，行军有你跟随，与军中不利。"
        },
        {
          "character": "袁绍",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "休出此不利之言！将人马拨与刘使君三千，归入后队。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘备下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "袁绍",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众将官，带马阵前去者！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（袁绍上马，下。四龙套、四文堂、四大刀手、文丑同随下。）"
        }
