      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、四大刀手、文丑同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "文丑",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "旌旗遮盖半壁天。\n刘备紧追马加鞭。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、刘备同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见文将军。"
        },
        {
          "character": "文丑",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "使君赶来何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "文将军，此去阵前，若遇我二弟云长，不可与他交战！"
        },
        {
          "character": "文丑",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我与你二弟云长，并不相认。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赤面长髯，就是我二弟，不可交战。"
        },
        {
          "character": "文丑",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "两军交锋，哪里顾得许多！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待备去到阵前，高坡之上，执一红灯，若是我二弟出马，我将红灯坠下，将军\n千万不可交战，备说他来降！"
        },
        {
          "character": "文丑",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，就依使君。请先过渡。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "备先行了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘备、四龙套同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "文丑",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "登舟去者。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、四大刀手、文丑同下。）"
