          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张辽、夏侯惇、乐进、徐晃、许褚、李典、曹洪、曹仁同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张辽",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "千军列队伍，万马扎团营。"
