          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（报子下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹仁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丞相，文丑讨战，待末将出马，生擒那文丑进帐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗯，小小年纪，出此狂言，还不坐下。\n二将军请！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖牌子〗。报子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "文丑营外骂阵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "再探！"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（报子下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唔呼呀，河北名将，一个个如此英勇，真名不虚传也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关羽怒。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗯，某看文丑，不是前来讨战，分明是前来送死！"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何出此言？"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "某在白马坡斩了颜良，文丑前来报仇。某不才愿讨一支将令，斩文丑首级，献\n与丞相。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军斩了颜良，又要出战，忒已劳倦。先命众将出马，倘若不胜，再请将军出\n战。\n众将官！粮草先行，人马在后。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐晃、张辽",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且慢，粮草先行，那厮劫去粮草，我军不战自乱。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老夫用兵之计，非汝等所知。徐晃、张辽，命你二人押粮前行，附耳上来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐晃、张辽",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张辽、徐晃同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众位将军，二队接杀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "夏侯惇、乐进、许褚、李典、曹洪、曹仁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（夏侯惇、乐进、许褚、李典、曹洪、曹仁同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二将军！众将不胜，将军出马不迟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丞相啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "赤兔战马声嘶喊，\n青龙偃月金光寒。\n河北的儿郎心胆寒。\n斩奸除恶不费难。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关羽、月华旗手、马童、大纛旗同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "关羽出营把文丑战，\n他中曹某激将言。\n但愿一战奏凯还！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
